---
/**
 * Inline equation. Use for symbol-only inserts like \(x^2\) where the
 * surrounding markdown's `$x^2$` syntax is fine — this exists to
 * provide an explicit JSX path for cases where the markdown parser
 * gets in the way.
 *
 * Defers actual rendering to KaTeX (rehype-katex when wired up). For
 * now this is a thin styling wrapper that respects the body type
 * size and family.
 */
---

<span class="prose-equation">
  <slot />
</span>
